4 SYNOPSIS:
5 Under existing law, there exists the Alabama
6 Office of Minority Affairs.
7 This bill would rename the office the Alabama
8 Office of Civic Engagement.
9 This bill would also make conforming changes.
10
11
12 A BILL
13 TO BE ENTITLED
14 AN ACT
15
16 Relating to the Alabama Office of Minority Affairs; to
17 amend Section 36-13-50, Code of Alabama 1975; to rename the
18 Alabama Office of Minority Affairs the Alabama Office of Civic
19 Engagement; to revise Sections 36-13-51, 36-13-53, 40-9F-38,
20 and 41-1-93, Code of Alabama 1975, to make conforming changes.
21 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
22 Section 1. Section 36-13-50, Code of Alabama, is
23 amended to read as follows:
24 "§36-13-50
25 There is established in state government the agency
26 that shall be known as the Alabama Office of Minority
27 AffairsCivic Engagement, to advise the Governor on issues
28 affecting minorities, including women, focusing on the
