43 employees for the office as he or she deems necessary to carry
44 out the duties and functions of the office. All employees of
45 the Governor who work in the Governor's Office of Minority
46 AffairsAlabama Office of Minority Affairs on July 1,
47 2022October 1, 2026, shall be transferred to the Alabama
48 Office of Minority AffairsCivic Engagement with no loss of
49 compensation or benefits. After July 1, 2022October 1, 2026,
50 the compensation of those employees shall be established by
51 the director in an amount that does not exceed the amount of
52 compensation paid to comparable state Merit System
53 classifications. All other employees of the office shall be
54 employed pursuant to the state Merit System.
55 (c) The director shall employ individuals in a manner
56 to assure the office staff is inclusive and reflects the
