132 "§41-1-93
133 Nothing in this article:
134 (1) Prevents student, staff, or faculty organizations
135 or associations from hosting diversity, equity, and inclusion
136 programs or discussions that may involve divisive concepts,
137 provided that no state funds are used to sponsor these
138 programs. If a student, staff, or faculty organization or
139 association hosts an event pursuant to this subdivision, it
140 shall identify the sponsor of the event at the event and in
